code: export default function variance(values,valueof){let count=0;let delta;let mean=0;let sum=0;if(valueof===undefined){for(let value of values){if(value!=null&&(value=+value)>=value){delta=value-mean;mean+=delta/++count;sum+=delta*(value-mean);}}}else{let index=-1;for(let value of values){if((value=valueof(value,++index,values))!=null&&(value=+value)>=value){delta=value-mean;mean+=delta/++count;sum+=delta*(value-mean);}}}if(count>1)return sum/(count-1);}
